Subscribe to this blog ' s feed April 23 , 2013 China rushes relief after Sichuan quake Saturday ' s earthquake in China ' s Sichuan province , measured by China ' s earthquake administration at magnitude 7 . 0 and by the U . S . Geological Survey at 6 . 6 , killed at least 192 people , injured more than 11 , 000 and left nearly two dozen missing , mostly in the rural communities around Ya ' an city .